{"tid":1633910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港《禁蒙面法》首2名被告, 被法官下達「宵禁令」","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:50:51.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"88a304c621498cdda3bf1eafd858d1829c5a7861","tid":1633910,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484725-20191007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484725-20191007.htm&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4pq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=d59e897a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484725-20191007.htm&h=cf2bbf22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484725-20191007.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 首宗違反禁蒙面法案押後再訊 兩被告准保釋<br />\n2019-10-07 HKT 11:18<br />\n<br />\n《禁止蒙面規例》生效後，首次有人被檢控，一男一女被控一項非法集結罪及一項違反禁止蒙面規例罪，案件早上在東區裁判法院提堂。兩人暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至11月18日，以待警方進一步調查，<strong>兩人分別獲准以現金300元及1000元保釋，期間不得離港、24小時內交出旅遊證件、並要遵守宵禁令，逢星期六需到觀塘警署報到。</strong><br />\n<br />\n兩名被告分別是一名18歲城市大學一年級學生、以及報稱無業的38歲女子，他們同被控在本年10月4及5日，在藍田啟田路一帶與其他不知名人士參與非法集結，並在10月5日無合法權限或合理辯解，而使用相當可能阻止識辨身分的蒙面物品，即掛耳式口罩。<br />\n<br />\n過百名戴上口罩、穿上黑衣的人士到場聲援，並在散庭後在法院外打開雨傘，多次高叫「蒙面無罪、立法無理」等口號。"},{"pid":"9990920ef5e3a841fc671ced897afdbc762c0693","tid":1633910,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"蒙下面都要宵禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225ddded06195e5cbc7e6ed087df27825250ec35","tid":1633910,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7503dcea2